  "title": "Sales Engineer #ESY",
  "description": "<p>• Conduct sales planning (Internal)</p><p>• Set and track sales goals and implement strategies for driving growth to achieve sales annual target.</p><p>• Maintain sales records and provide monthly sales pipeline.</p><p>• Provide capex planning (external) to the client.</p><p>• Develop and nurture strong relationships with existing clients to understand their requirements, preferences, and pain points.</p><p>• Propose solutions and sales presentations to showcase the value and address client questions head-on.</p><p>• Negotiate terms, pricing, and Letter of Awards with clients to secure deals while ensuring profitability for the company.</p><p>• Convert leads into sales by resolving client concerns and guiding them through the purchasing process.</p><p>• Provide ongoing support to existing clients while ensuring their satisfaction and fostering long-term relationships.</p><p>• Stay current with industry trends, competitor activities, and customer feedback to identify new opportunities for improvement.</p><p>• Work closely with cross-functional teams to align efforts, leverage resources, and maximize sales opportunities.</p><p>• Ensure compliance to Organizational Norms, policies, procedures, and requirements of the Sales process.<br /></p><p><br />Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p><br /></p>",
